{"tw": {"2696050": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "YARISUTEMESUBUTA ~ 一次性交易大師 ~", "steam_appid": 2696050, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3171570, 3593650], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過150隻以上的怪獸!!內容豐富度爆表的超大型RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >訓練你的怪獸，以冠軍作為目標吧!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的夥伴才有的超級密技「作弊衝撞」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >必定先攻且一擊必殺，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >簡單模式下還可以無限使用!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.poster.avif?t=1774540455\" width=598 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.webm?t=1774540455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.mp4?t=1774540455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/e23efea781bc07883110418ef3aae552.webp?t=1774540455\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這個世界存在著「Yarimon」這種不可思議的生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被排擠的主角和最弱Yarimon，這就是我們...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不過這都是之前的事情了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為夥伴的Yarimon居然突然學會了威力800000的「作弊衝撞」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界不一樣了...只要使用這個技能不管事什麼樣的對手都能打倒...(雖然一場戰鬥中只能使用一次)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當然，光靠這樣就想要當上冠軍還太天真了，作為訓練家就必須不斷精進自己的技巧，但就算是這樣，對於第一次擊敗兒時玩伴的我已經是非常開心的事情了，終於可以把一些輸掉的錢給拿回來...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然後，我也隨波逐流地踏上了冒險之旅(被兒時玩伴用「我要去旅行了，你也給我去旅行」的壓力逼迫)。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.poster.avif?t=1774540455\" width=596 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.webm?t=1774540455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.mp4?t=1774540455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅行的途中，我慢慢的接觸到這世界的謎團...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我的冒險正式開始了!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朝著Yarimon圖鑑完全制霸為目標!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.poster.avif?t=1774540455\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.webm?t=1774540455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.mp4?t=1774540455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/0571469e14ccf4be1c12270501251fe7.webp?t=1774540455\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪獸收集型戰鬥RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各式各樣的「Yarimon」、朝著冠軍努力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是跟野生的Yari